WEBVTT

00:03:29.909 --> 00:03:32.537
of course at first I resist them,

00:03:32.561 --> 00:03:35.785
but then I remember
what I learned from the mothers:

00:03:35.809 --> 00:03:37.142
stay open.

00:03:37.508 --> 00:03:38.937
Stay curious.

00:03:38.961 --> 00:03:41.666
Ask the pain what it's come to deliver.

00:03:42.017 --> 00:03:44.475
Something new wants to be born.

00:03:45.311 --> 00:03:47.609
And there was one more big soulful lesson,

00:03:47.633 --> 00:03:50.427
and that one I learned
from Albert Einstein.

00:03:50.769 --> 00:03:52.725
He wasn't at any of the births, but --

00:03:52.749 --> 00:03:53.781
(Laughter)

00:03:53.805 --> 00:03:56.447
It was a lesson about time.

00:03:57.732 --> 00:04:01.885
At the end of his life,
Albert Einstein concluded